<h1>Problem 1431 - 2021 IMOSL, A3</h1>
<h2 class='difficulty'>Difficulty: 6</h2>
<p>Given a positive integer \(n\), find the smallest value of \[\left\lfloor \frac{a_1}{1} \right\rfloor + \left\lfloor{\frac{a_2}{2}}\right\rfloor + \cdots + \left\lfloor{\frac{a_n}{n}}\right\rfloor\] over all permutations \((a_1,\dots,a_n)\) of \((1,\dots,n).\)</p>
